Package: OAmonitor
Type: Package
Title: Scoring Open Accessibility of Publications at Dutch Universities
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Barbara M.I. Vreede, Kristina M. Hettne
Maintainer: Barbara Vreede <b.m.i.vreede@uu.nl>
Description: An automated workflow using both local and remote (DOAJ and Unpaywall API) data
    on a database of publications, with the aim to determine their public accessibility, and report
    on the varying Open Access states (Green, Gold, Hybrid) of publications.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0) 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.1
Imports:
